    "Per i bug, KidBox allega automaticamente i log diagnostici dell'app (gli stessi usati per i crash report).": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "For bugs, KidBox automatically attaches the app's diagnostic logs (the same ones used for crash reports)."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Para los errores, KidBox adjunta automáticamente los registros de diagnóstico de la app (los mismos que se usan para los informes de fallos)."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pour les bugs, KidBox joint automatiquement les journaux de diagnostic de l'app (les mêmes que pour les rapports de plantage)."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Per il controllo sicurezza password (Have I Been Pwned), KidBox usa k-anonymity: invia solo i primi 5 caratteri dell'hash SHA-1, mai la password in chiaro.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "For the password security check (Have I Been Pwned), KidBox uses k-anonymity: it sends only the first 5 characters of the SHA-1 hash, never the plaintext password."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Para la comprobación de seguridad de contraseñas (Have I Been Pwned), KidBox usa k-anonymity: solo envía los 5 primeros caracteres del hash SHA-1, nunca la contraseña en claro."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pour la vérification de sécurité des mots de passe (Have I Been Pwned), KidBox utilise le k-anonymity : il n'envoie que les 5 premiers caractères du hachage SHA-1, jamais le mot de passe en clair."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Per selezionare un contatto, abilita l'accesso ai contatti nelle impostazioni.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "To select a contact, enable contacts access in settings."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Para seleccionar un contacto, activa el acceso a los contactos en los ajustes."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pour sélectionner un contact, activez l'accès aux contacts dans les réglages."
          }
        }
      }
    },
